name: QoS Thong
description:
Inspired by: https://civitai.com/models/47301/qos-underwear

Great on 512x768, 768x512, 768x768

Use prompt: qos-thong to trigger it.

Then you can alter it further by:

pink-thong

white-thong

black-thong

green-thong

yellow-thong

brown-thong

Works great from 0.65 to 0.80 weight.

Some might require different weights. I ran it on several checkpoints to stress test.
